name.content: Campanile Val de France (Ex Kyriad Disneyland)

description.content: The hotel invites guests to enjoy a cosy, peaceful and relaxing atmosphere for families. The CDG Airport is at a 40 kilometres, around a 40 minute's car drive and downtown Paris (the Tour Eiffel, Champs-Elysées) is at about 50 kilometres. The hotel has many rooms in two buildings of two floors with lift. Rooms designed with a double bed or twin beds and most feature bunk beds. The rooms have air conditioning, the bathrooms are all equipped with a bath, shower and a hairdryer. With 3 soundproofed meeting rooms, air-conditioned, lit by daylight and able to accommodate up to 200 people, Hotel Campanile Val de France, situated in Disneyland® Paris, is the ideal place for your meetings.
